Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！ 那麼今天就這樣結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為白天變得比較短了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在天黑之前回到家裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 玩去吧 玩去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}玩什麼去啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站前的那個 要去嘗嘗麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 美緒也一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 已經回去了麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一聲沒吭就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算不算是對相生同學做了件壞事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能再稍微 像普通的女生一樣打招呼就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我… 我叫東雲名乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聽我說啊 那個… 這個發條啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為家附近的咖啡店改裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以進去看了看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您點些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來杯濃縮咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高杯的濃縮咖啡 可以麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}トール{\r\fs36}：Tall，指高杯，與{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}透（とおる）{\r\fs36}同音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透… 透明！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T是指… 透明麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 要喝T的濃縮咖啡嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 T的濃縮咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SMALL的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮杯的濃縮咖啡 可以麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}ショート：{\r\fs36} Short，指矮杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SMALL的短杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好… 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 濃縮咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有加熱或者加冰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就加熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果點熱的的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SIZE得是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOLO或…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}DOPPIO：意大利語，相當於DOUBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DO… DOPPIO！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO是什… 什… 麼啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO x 3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO是什麼… 什麼東西啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:31.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\fnsimhei\b1\pos(662,475)\c&H8DAFED&}本日的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啦 剛才忘啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想點這個「本日的咖啡」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃縮咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有SOLO和…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO的 請問您要哪種
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO的 請問您要哪種
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊～…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那個 就請你適當看著辦吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您點的濃縮咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級… 苦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後還是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買自動售貨機的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:43.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\frz270\shad2\pos(1180,360)\4c&HCED7D9&}CATCH BALL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫子小美過生日的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給他買了個手套作為禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 我要扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒哦誒 小美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離那麼遠的話是夠不到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然這麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然孫子真是好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法吶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情地扔過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也想稍微展示一下帥氣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下墜球…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,0)\frz270\bord5\blur8\pos(1220,360)}TICOMART
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H3D3E3C&\frz6.951\pos(632,154)}悶絕！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\shad0\bord0\c&H3D3E3C&\frz6.951\pos(286,383)}滾燙滾燙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\shad0\bord0\c&H3D3E3C&\frz6.951\pos(308,498)}大廚的心血來潮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\shad0\bord0\c&H3D3E3C&\pos(554,652)}雞肉棒——50元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我來一根這個「悶絕滾燙滾燙大廚的心血來潮雞肉棒」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小治郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕快 受理快要結…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美～緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小祐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班會開完之後 等我發現 你已經沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是… 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始也不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是… 我接下來 有點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 說的這麼重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是… 怎麼說呢… 嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說嘛 說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}可以打擾一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是抱歉啦——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 小祐！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像 一不小心就道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我也嚇了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一上來就被人道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 有什麼事情麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 最近有好幾起自動售貨機裡出現假鈔的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想問問你們看沒看到什麼可疑人物之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒 你怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒怎麼走過這邊吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據目擊情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人帶著一個有紅色條紋的茶色手提袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不尋常的反應！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…帶著麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假鈔… 帶著呢麼！？
